# Relaxation of MgZn2 intermetallic

units           metal
atom_style      atomic
boundary        p p p

read_data       znmg2.data

pair_style      meam/c
pair_coeff      * * library.meam Zn Mg ZnMg.meam Zn Mg

neighbor        2.0 bin
neigh_modify    delay 10 check yes

thermo          50
thermo_style    custom step pe etotal lx ly lz press

min_style       cg
minimize        1e-8 1e-8 10000 10000

write_data      znmg2_relaxed.data